mike s zafirovski  wikipedia mike s zafirovski from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search mike s zafirovski zafirovski at a conference in las vegas born c  skopje socialist federal republic of yugoslavia nationality macedonian american education bachelor of arts in mathematics from edinboro university honorary doctorate in public service from edinboro university mike s zafirovski born c  is a macedonian american business executive contents  personal life  career  see also  references personal lifeedit zafirovski was born in skopje socialist federal republic of yugoslavia the presentday capital of the republic of macedonia he immigrated to united states in  arriving in cleveland ohio with his family  among them and speaking no english two years later he entered edinboro university on a swimming scholarship in  he received the ellis island medal of honor careeredit zafirovski spent  years with general electric starting in  where he went through ges jack welchstyle leadership training programs and served in various management positions between  and  he was head of the european division of ge lighting during which time the division posted record profits he was then promoted to his last position at ge as president and ceo of ge lighting from july  to may  afterwards he joined motorola serving as executive vice president and president of the personal communications sector from june  until july  in  he was passed over for the promotion to chief operating officer for edward breen but breen quit later that year and zafirovski was given the title in july  his success in the pcs division among other achievements at motorola seemed to make him a perfect candidate for the ceo position but the title went to edward zander on january   zafirovski resigned on january   he was a consultant to and a director of motorola from then until may  when zafirovski was chosen to head up nortel networks in early october motorola filed a suit against him alleging that his new position would break the terms of the nondisclosure agreement he had signed as part of that agreement he had received a payoff from motorola the payoff had a clawback element should zafirovski return to work within a defined period he would agree to refund a percentage of the payoff the problem was he did not want to refund any of the money as a consequence nortel agreed to pay  million on his behalf zafirovski became the president and chief executive officer of nortel networks replacing bill owens as of november   zafirovski announced he was stepping down as ceo of nortel on august   following the sale of the companys cdma and lte businesses to ericsson as part of a bankruptcy restructuring process he was elected to the board of directors at boeing on october   in july  president george w bush appointed zafirovski to the national security telecommunications advisory committee in august  mike zafirovski sought a  million payout from nortel while employees who worked for years with the company lost their jobs with no compensation at all  see alsoedit nortel motorola referencesedit  umd interview  nortel bio of mike which the statements native of macedonia and zafirovski serves on  the macedonian arts council  mike zafirovski ceo of nortel networks corporation pa state system of higher education website archived from the original on  retrieved    mclean catherine  mr fixit takes on his biggest challenge globeandmailcom toronto retrieved    all medalists  neco website retrieved  dead link  mutschler ann motorola president coo zafirovski to resign edncom retrieved    mcmillan robert motorola nortel settle zafirovski dispute infoworldcom retrieved    nortels zafirovski resigns as asset sales near end update bloomberg    archived copy archived from the original on  retrieved    motorolas mike zafirovski elected to boeing board of directors boeing press releases archived from the original on  retrieved    httpwwwcanadacomtopicsnewsstoryhtmlidcebecdddafd  httpwwwncsgovnsta